**3-Year ROI:** 35-52% on upfront investment

### **Regulatory/Governance Considerations**

1. **STS Eligibility:**

- Programme can be STS-eligible if pools meet criteria
- Simplicity test applies at series level
- Specialist lender can be STS if criteria met (prime BTL generally can)
- **Benefit:** 15-20bps pricing improvement on senior notes

1. **Capital Treatment:**

- If client is regulated (FCA/PRA): Check Securitization Regulation
- Significant Risk Transfer (SRT) assessment per series
- Programme structure doesn’t change SRT analysis
- **Action:** Pre-clear with regulator if applicable

1. **Tax Efficiency:**

- SPV should be “orphan” (no group link)
- UK tax-transparent for income pass-through
- Stamp duty exemption via Schedule 19 FA 2003
- **Check:** If client has Irish/offshore origination, consider Irish Section 110 SPV

