|**Master Issuer**    |£4.7-6.9m      |£7.9-11.8m |**£12.6-18.7m**|**26-38bps** |
|**NET SAVINGS**      |(£0.6m) - £0.4m|£5.7-10.0m |**£5.1-9.7m**  |**10-20bps** |

